'''Madelein Aurin''' was the [[Author/Legends|author]] of ''[[Heroes Of The Republic]]'', a book that chronicled some of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic's]] most visible figures. The book was eventually banned by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].<ref name="Divoran">''{{WEGCite|story=The Divoran Holochess Players|book=Galaxy Guide 9: Fragments from the Rim}}''</ref>

